Shehu Sani, the Senator representing Kaduna Central has reacted to Alhaji Aliko Dangote’s appointment to APC’s Presidential Campaign Council for the 2019 elections. Presidential spokesperson, Femi Adesina in a statement disclosed  the  appointment of  Alhaji Aliko Dangote and Mr. Femi Otedola as members of its Presidential Campaign Council for the 2019 elections. Shehu Sani in a tweet said: “Dear Bro Aliko,don’t use Broom to reinforce your silos,don’t use Broom as your plasterboard;don’t use Broom to mix your concrete,maintain the use of your machine concrete mixer”. Dear Bro Aliko,don’t use Broom to reinforce your silos,don’t use Broom as your plasterboard;don’t use Broom to mix your concrete,maintain the use of your machine concrete mixer. — Senator Shehu Sani (@ShehuSani) December 28, 2018  Sanusi receives staff of office, traditional regalia FG commends Dangote’s mining initiative APC appoints Dangote, Otedola members of Buhari's campaign committee